Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================A-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,得快點 把那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,給我停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,被那傢伙到達神樹 我們的世界會消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣就好 一起消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,才不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,御靈！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉 也有人一無所知的活著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是不能放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因為那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你要說那才是勇者嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,和其他人沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如果沒法保護最重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,成為勇者就沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我提不起勁頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈… 你要是就那樣老實待著就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要是睡過去 就一切都解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,已經太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥不會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的活地獄沒有盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因為有東鄉在一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,無論多麼痛苦 東鄉都由我來保護！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,會忘掉寶貴的心情和回憶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能不要緊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,連友奈和大家的事情也會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒法乖乖放棄認命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要失去最重要的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼能這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,無比強烈的這樣想！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我們當時…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定也這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,現在只記得好悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,都不知道自己的淚水有什麼意義！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊 我怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈肯定也會忘記我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不是騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不是騙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我會永遠和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來 就不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不要丟下我一個人～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,太陽…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我闖了大禍…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不是東鄉的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要阻止那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,給我停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,停不下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不要放棄…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼能在這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,腿…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,已經… 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小樹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 在這麼關鍵的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,推回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,三個人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凜！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不要小看勇者部！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 勇者部！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,贊州中學勇者部！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者・結城友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,到達吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,結束了… 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:10:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！ 友奈！ 友奈！ 友奈！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的戰鬥不是夢裡的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.67,Notice,,0,0,0,,大規模的山火基本被控制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,從實際發生的大規模災害也可以知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,向神樹大人 拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我們所守護 所奪回的日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下等一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,姐… 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真的取回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會痊癒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:14.75,Notice,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs25}發件人：大赦\N收件人：三好夏凜\N主題　：神諭\N\N敵人的來襲會暫時中止。\N失去精靈的你，也失去了勇者的力量。\N請繼續學生生活。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,從那以後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,大赦的聯絡一直是單方面的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒法回信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是被神樹大人解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,已經不需要我們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,失去目的了 會不安？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不許笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 外面的世界仍然是那樣沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,希望我們的戰鬥數據能派上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的戰鬥不是無謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以神樹大人才不再尋求祭品了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來只有相信後輩 交給她們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 勇者部是不滅的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,被你搶先說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,只有那孩子沒醒來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,因為那孩子… 一個人努力過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,犧牲自己不要緊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這種想法… 我討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 要不是那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,今天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩又說了奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我們來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,午安 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這是壓花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 犧牲了最重要的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我做出了那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不許說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是任何人的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不是討論過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 距離文化祭已經沒幾天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,關於今後的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我想把友奈的角色就那樣保留著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的腿都治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈一定也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想那麼冷血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我也沒有那麼冷血啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,戲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,戲劇先繼續練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.71,0:15:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,相信友奈她 一定… 一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:25.64,Notice,,0,0,0,,致明日的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者無論怎麼受傷 怎麼受傷 都決不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,因為如果所有人都放棄掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這個世界只會陷入黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者相信 自己不放棄就能激勵到大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,也有人看不起這樣的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者只是淡淡的一笑了之
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,也有人說沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,儘管如此 勇者也沒有氣餒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,大家接二連三的向魔王屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不知不覺 勇者只剩孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者只剩一個人這件事 沒人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,即使只剩一個人 勇者也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者也… 沒有放棄戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因為只要不放棄 希望就不會結束…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,無論失去什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就算如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想失去最重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就算再寂寞 再痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是說也要和我一直在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,東… 鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我都和你在一起 一直
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:17:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉 我都聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉的聲音 大家的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,結城友奈 讓大家擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.63,Notice,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 友奈！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,大家沒事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我好擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,會不會醒不過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是不怎麼擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我也以為已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,用韌性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.18,0:19:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,韌性？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是神樹大人救了你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈肯定是憑自己的力量回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不是奇跡或神的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈是用自己的強烈意志和韌性回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:20:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者相信自己的不屈會激勵大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 因為有大家在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,因為相信著大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,所以自己不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,到頭來世上都是討厭的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,都是痛苦的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你也裝作沒看見 墮落吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不要抵抗了 被冰冷的現實凍僵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那種事是心情決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,只要重視對方就能成為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,只要心心相印 就能變強無數倍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,韌性會無限地湧出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然世上有很多討厭的事情 悲傷的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:21:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,自己無可奈何的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但只要有最喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就不可能氣餒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.69,0:21:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,因為有最喜歡的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,無論多少次都能站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者絕對不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.98,0:21:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.73,0:21:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:21:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,頭有點暈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.16,0:22:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.06,0:22:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼困難都能克服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.14,0:22:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,和最喜歡的大家一起的話
